data.description: ***INCENTIVES! If buyer's use seller's preferred lender, lender will pay an  $3000 towards buyers closing cost. ***.  Located on a desirable treed corner lot. Property offers 2700 sq ft of living space, not including finished lower level, open concept, 4 beds, 2 full baths,2 half baths, office, 1st flr laundry, formal dining/  living room. Kitchen opens to great room. Primary suite has walk-in closet, bath w/ quartz countertops, double sinks, and heated floor. Large bonus room overlooks the vaulted great room w/ floor to ceiling brick fireplace and skylights. The finished lower level adds a spacious recreational area and 1/2 bath. Sprawling deck and gazebo is the perfect outdoor entertainment space! (front load washer/dryer convey).
